Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.26,0:00:22.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.98,0:00:31.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我永遠注視著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何  我如此  三生有幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.12,0:00:47.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每見到水平線  便有莫名哀傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.21,0:00:56.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠遠地回首 過去的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.80,0:01:00.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限感傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.93,0:01:06.91,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.06,0:01:13.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠深入思考的只有  Mystery
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.57,0:01:19.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  命中的良人就在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.95,0:01:26.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我  一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.71,0:01:34.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我  一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.33,0:20:58.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想嘗試如履薄冰般危險的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.59,0:21:05.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好希望心中描繪的夢想能夠成型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.34,0:21:09.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever My Destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.60,0:21:16.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空船如果降臨在自己面前 我一定會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.81,0:21:23.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋下朋友  離開地球展開旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.78,0:21:32.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說平靜的每一天就是幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.54,0:21:42.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我其實想逃  我害怕沒有你的每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.84,0:21:51.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像如履薄冰般  偷偷地  戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.43,0:21:57.91,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心飛向你的速度比光速更快更遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.06,0:22:01.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever My Destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.33,0:00:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人與人的邂逅充滿了神奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.13,0:00:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種刑案更是謎題重重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.63,0:00:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠遇到你真的是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.67,0:00:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的是真正的暗號文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.43,0:00:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內行的看門道 外行的看熱鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.93,0:00:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.73,0:00:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.73,0:00:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.01,0:01:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新名任太郎的女兒新名香保裏晚上突然來訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.02,0:01:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的是拜託叔叔尋找她的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.81,0:01:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新名老師和他夫人在兩個月前就失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.48,0:01:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小說還是能夠傳真到出版社去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.74,0:01:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們立即去了出版社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.53,0:02:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在新名老師寫的小說裡發現了反常的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.04,0:02:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個求救的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.54,0:02:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.09,0:02:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.22,0:02:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些台詞裡果然隱藏著關於新名老師的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.73,0:02:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來那篇充滿挑釁意味的序言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.07,0:02:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有作者會在作品裡出場和那些奇怪的台詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.07,0:02:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都可以說得通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.51,0:02:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.91,0:02:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個把新名老師和他夫人囚禁起來的歹徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.91,0:02:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目的到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.73,0:02:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推理小說家失蹤事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.83,0:02:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 什麼 你是不是又想到什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也沒有什麼大不了的啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 文藝時代編輯部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.76,0:03:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這篇稿子裡每一句話開頭的字都是1/2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你知道暗號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說他已經解開暗號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我把員警叫到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個關西口音的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關西口音的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.82,0:03:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 你們要我說幾遍啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你們快叫員警來 聽到沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.29,0:03:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是服部吧 我是目暮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.33,0:03:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 是警官你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.73,0:03:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在啥地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.93,0:03:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好久沒見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.13,0:03:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是暗號啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.43,0:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經解開了這部小說裡面隱藏的1/2頂點這個暗號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.73,0:03:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到書上的序言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也被這個臭老頭的話弄得滿肚子火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看著看著就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.48,0:03:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實出現在小說裡面的作者新名先生所說的台詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.23,0:03:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是引導我們進入這個謎題的一種暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台詞就是暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.36,0:03:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.15,0:04:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段序言其實並不是想對我們這些讀者進行挑釁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作者在這部小說裡隱藏了某種資訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.66,0:04:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是希望會有人來破解的一種求救信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說你已經把這個暗號的內容解開了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.25,0:04:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 我已經把一開始的那部分暗號解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.30,0:04:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一章裡的關鍵就是這部小說的標題《1/2的頂點》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.05,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以看到所有台詞的最上面一個字全都是1/2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.81,0:04:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是兩個字可以合成為一個字的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個字合成為一個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把這個規律記住再從頭開始看的話就會發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.11,0:04:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“力”加“目”是“助”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.94,0:04:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“十”加“1”是“け”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“C”加“一”是“て”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.82,0:04:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到最後這裡“ノ”加“1”形成的就是“レ”這個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前的“く”和“他”我雖然還不是很確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過把“他”這個字想成“不想有其他的”這個意思的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該也可以說得通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把這些字連起來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.83,0:05:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.53,0:05:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,け
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.13,0:05:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,て
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,く
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.33,0:05:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,レ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂快來救救我＂ 是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.39,0:05:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我想這位作家一直被關在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人逼迫著寫這部小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才會採取這種方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才不會引起歹徒的注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.32,0:05:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能把他的求救信號傳達給讀者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.74,0:05:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這是作者時隔十年之久的最新力作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個歹徒很可能是一位狂熱的粉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.29,0:05:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是企圖奪取暢銷小說家的稿費而謀取不義之財的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.59,0:05:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部小說的稿費已經付了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有 在我們開始連載這部小說之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.22,0:05:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新名老師就表示寫完之後才告訴我們匯款帳號的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.35,0:05:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 我們就從可疑的稿件開始查起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.89,0:05:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我還沒有把所有的暗號解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.64,0:05:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 警官 警官 我說警官啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你到哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧不起人也要有個限度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我說服部啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.16,0:06:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你注意到新名老師其他的台詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.79,0:06:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦　是工藤啊 你怎麼會在那裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 純粹只是巧合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.04,0:06:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說也是啊 我們兩個都是屬於同一類的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.42,0:06:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會這麼巧又有機會碰面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說暗號吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 要不要到大阪來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.30,0:06:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到我這裡好吃的烏龍麵要多少有多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們東京的味道太重 難吃死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.35,0:06:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要掛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.02,0:06:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊對不起 對不起 還是來說暗號吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然開頭部分的暗號我完全解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是接下來的那些台詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就根本不能用1/2的頂點這個原則來解釋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把開頭的字一字排開的話 得到的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.43,0:06:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 他 か ぃ へ 今 居 白 レ ノ 所 犯 人 わ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把第二個“他”字去掉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.37,0:07:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能通到第三個字啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.88,0:07:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果硬要把“へ”和“今”連起來也沒法變成一個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.05,0:07:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子我們要解開這個暗號的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還少了很多必要的輔助棋子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.97,0:07:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 躲過我們兩個偵探眼睛的重要的棋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定隱藏在某個地方才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.69,0:07:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部 你怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都在那兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.40,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要我在大阪這兒瞎操什麼心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.11,0:07:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 工藤 接下來就交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.32,0:07:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道了什麼就聯絡我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可要好好加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.29,0:07:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我們找服部來解其他的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.67,0:07:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.92,0:07:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我掛的 是服部哥哥自己...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 這裡是東京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.13,0:07:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就別去管那個大阪的混小子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們自己來解決問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 說的也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你差不多該睡了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我睡覺幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.78,0:08:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是每次重要關頭都會睡起覺來的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.24,0:08:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可是我現在還不睏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.41,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來救救我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會把香保裏小姐的父母都找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們大家一起來動動腦筋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.80,0:08:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 無論怎麼把旁邊的文字加上去或者去掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都得不到完整的句子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.81,0:08:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個暗號到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不知道暗號的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.44,0:08:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有綁架新名老師的歹徒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒既然把他囚禁了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.57,0:08:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該會注意到他寫的文章才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒如果是老師的粉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於老師一反常態的序言以及作者親自登場這兩點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.41,0:09:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是注意到了才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來一開始的那個求救暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該解開了才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 他的目的就是稿費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.53,0:09:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.26,0:09:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這筆稿費並不是什麽钜款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.97,0:09:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是歹徒囚禁他兩個月的目的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不通啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.35,0:09:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒的企圖和暗號到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.77,0:09:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這個地方不對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師想要表現一下寫點法語倒也沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個詞好像拼錯了喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法語？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.99,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“幽默”的拼法應該是humour
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.63,0:09:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡少了一個h
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看到這個字再實際唸過以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.63,0:09:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能瞭解爲什麼會拼錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.93,0:09:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣 原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 這個暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能解...能解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以一字不漏地解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新名老師被歹徒囚禁起來的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就是那裡沒錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.23,0:10:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 我們發覺剛剛傳過來的第八章的故事裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有新名老師的幾句台詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.82,0:10:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.86,0:10:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這一幕裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不快一點救他們的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新名老師和夫人就會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 只有用老辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.26,0:10:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這手錶麻醉槍讓叔叔睡著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 我來為你介紹一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位就是我們的總編輯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打..打偏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.28,0:10:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 沒別的辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.03,0:11:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總編輯 總編輯 你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.37,0:11:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今也只有利用他來充當偵探了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.58,0:11:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得用變聲器轉到總編輯的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.75,0:11:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總編輯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.43,0:11:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽過這個傢夥的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這個地方幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在玩捉迷藏啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.02,0:11:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 麻醉針只有一根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來只有等叔叔他們把暗號解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.98,0:11:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快點的話 新名老師他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.78,0:11:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了啊 快點起來啊 總編輯 總編輯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.62,0:11:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然打起瞌睡來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.32,0:11:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像沈睡的小五郎一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.42,0:11:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.63,0:11:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小鬼笑什麼笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.38,0:12:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為總編輯叔叔睡覺的樣子跟叔叔一模一樣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.89,0:12:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這個人還真有點Humour呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼Humour
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.81,0:12:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小鬼怎麼會知道這麼多奇怪的辭彙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.85,0:12:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是剛才那邊的叔叔說過的詞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們剛才不就是在說Humour什麼的 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這個編輯把法語的“幽默”給拼錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才就是在幫他更正啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我忘記把H加上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扯這個幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這些法國人真的好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.12,0:12:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有H這個字母 但是H又不發音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不發音的話那乾脆把H去掉不就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆把H...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.51,0:12:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我聽你們說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.97,0:12:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這部小說裡出現的新名老師就住在法國吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.89,0:12:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利老弟 難道這會是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.23,0:12:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這就是解讀這個暗號的另一個關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說開頭雖然有H但是不發音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.99,0:13:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種是法語裡特有的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聲H
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.87,0:13:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H 這麽說凡是H開頭的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是ハ行字母開頭的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他要我們把ハ、ヒ、フ、ヘ、ホ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾個字母開頭的字都去掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.29,0:13:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據1/2的頂點裡所有可以配成對的每一個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把ハ行字母開頭的字去掉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.05,0:13:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就可以把一開始的那個“他”字給去掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.60,0:13:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1/2的頂點 再配上無聲H這個公式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把新名先生在第二章出場的這一幕的台詞加以解讀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我（私）”和“他（hoka）”是“我（私）”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.36,0:13:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“ぃ”和“カ”是“が”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.23,0:13:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“へ（he）”和“今”是“今”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“居”和“白（haku）”是“居”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.65,0:13:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“レ”和“ノ”是“ル”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“所”和“犯（han）”是“所”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.16,0:13:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“人（hito）”和“わ”是“わ”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部連起來就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.24,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我目前所在的地方是（私が今居ル所わ）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是“我目前所在的地方”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 真的可以連成句子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,は之所以用わ來代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是怕它因爲無聲H的公式而被去掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.51,0:14:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 如果照這個樣子把新名先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.26,0:14:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第三章出場的那一幕的台詞加以解讀的話 那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.81,0:14:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木 戶 市 立 大 飯 店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.27,0:14:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木戶市立大飯店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.94,0:14:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼飯店啊 聽都沒聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.65,0:14:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜應該是用日式羅馬字母來做標記的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.41,0:14:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.12,0:14:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふ就不是用HU 而是FU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說一開始的那個字不用去掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不”加“木”就是“杯”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.79,0:14:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說就是杯戶市立大飯店了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四章的台詞應該就是他所在的房間號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.59,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二 四 零 七 號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在就在二四零七號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.77,0:15:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我們現在立刻趕到杯戶市立大飯店2407號房去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.07,0:15:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您先看一下這份稿子 上面好像還有台詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.32,0:15:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是剛才傳過來的第八章的稿子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.00,0:15:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.13,0:15:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點 沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.53,0:15:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 動作快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.17,0:15:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杯戶市立大飯店 跟著前面的巡邏車就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.51,0:15:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽 爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.03,0:16:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們千萬不要有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.13,0:16:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還活著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“沒有時間了”的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說危險雖然迫近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是應該還有緩衝的餘地才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那份稿子傳到出版社的時間算起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在為止還沒有超過1小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小說又寫到一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.60,0:16:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我認爲你父母活著的可能性很高 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.03,0:16:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不明白的是歹徒的目的何在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.95,0:16:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的是期待偵探左文字系列作品的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個激進分子所為嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.37,0:16:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.25,0:16:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼歹徒的目的是想搶奪稿費嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.13,0:16:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這家飯店的24層是高級套房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就劃不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.13,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個歹徒的目的到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.35,0:16:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然新名老師連簽名都沒辦法簽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.43,0:16:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓他繼續寫小說的意圖是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 如果他不能夠簽名的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.19,0:17:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示他是用口述的方法請人幫他輸入文字處理機裡的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.40,0:17:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只要一個字打錯的話 整個意思就都錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.70,0:17:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這帶有暗號的文章難道是請人代打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.33,0:17:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則文章隨時可能遭到扭曲或是刪字漏詞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上不會有這種明知故犯的傢夥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算請他的夫人代爲打字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視他們的人也一定會發現才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.73,0:17:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.73,0:17:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這次的案件...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2407號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡沒錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意歹徒身上很可能攜帶武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要提高警覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.97,0:18:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香保裏 妳怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 請你讓開一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動 我們是員警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.43,0:18:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.43,0:18:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊剛剛才嚥下最後一口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.29,0:18:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來遲了一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.17,0:18:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香保裏小姐 其實我們一直打電話到妳家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就是找不到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.43,0:18:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那個綁架新名先生的歹徒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.01,0:18:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.76,0:19:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生是我丈夫多年來的主治醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那歹徒到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有什麼歹徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.69,0:19:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要說有的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.40,0:19:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該要算現在躺在那裡的我的丈夫 新名他本人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 那個暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.78,0:19:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.99,0:19:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是我丈夫製造的假像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.62,0:19:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他爲什麼要這麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫生前經常這麼對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.96,0:19:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到最幸福的那個瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.26,0:19:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是我所完成的作品受到讀者的稱讚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.93,0:19:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作家我當了四十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.03,0:19:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻還有一種幸福沒感受過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.89,0:19:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這輩子只有這麼一次我也希望看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.10,0:19:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀者在我說出答案之前就將謎題解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種充滿自信和得意的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.11,0:19:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月前我丈夫就告訴我他希望能在死之前達成這個願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.49,0:19:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我就跟主治醫生兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.41,0:20:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬到這裡來協助我丈夫完成這部小說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.37,0:20:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是癌症晚期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.88,0:20:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個星期前連手也動不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.63,0:20:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以稿子上的簽名才用複印的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.30,0:20:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 香保裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.93,0:20:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓這個暗號更具真實性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳爸爸才交待我們絕對不要告訴妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.03,0:20:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.98,0:20:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就當這是妳爸爸生前最後的一次任性吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.10,0:20:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒他好嗎 香保裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.63,0:22:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來這件事情還真是勞師動眾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.75,0:22:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者寫下那種暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.23,0:22:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道要是弄不好就會驚動員警的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.76,0:22:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.23,0:22:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想看到讀者充滿自信和得意的表情那句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.77,0:22:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以一直會刊登在新名老師的小說後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.44,0:22:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就表示他一直在等那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.43,0:22:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有位讀者到他面前對他說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.23,0:22:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把謎題解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.58,0:22:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過搞了半天誰也沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.28,0:22:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看這部暢銷小說也就要因爲新名老師的死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.62,0:22:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而跟著一起結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.83,0:22:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會結束的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.25,0:22:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼續寫下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.79,0:22:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會用新名任太郎的名字繼續寫下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.47,0:22:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這件事情發生的兩個月之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.14,0:23:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香保裏小姐成功地完成了她父親的這部小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.56,0:23:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《1/2的頂點》的單行本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.18,0:23:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了最暢銷的小說之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.98,0:23:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著這部小說也順理成章地拍成了電視劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.93,0:23:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且得到了好評
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.73,0:23:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此她繼承了她父親的事業 走上了小說家的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.86,0:23:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說最主要的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.57,0:23:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因爲她的才華遠遠淩駕於她父親之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.49,0:23:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小說故事的後半段她又加上了三個左文字的助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.16,0:23:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個糊塗的偵探 一個任性的年輕女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.37,0:23:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個就是戴著眼鏡的狂妄少年三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.03,0:23:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以誰為範本的就不用說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我是狂妄少年也太過分了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.33,0:23:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.93,0:23:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過去啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.73,0:24:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很明顯的殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.23,0:24:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.53,0:24:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就設計好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.63,0:24:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.23,0:24:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.03,0:24:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.63,0:24:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模型手槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.33,0:24:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是10月12日播映
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.43,0:24:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊看少年Sunday 一邊耐心等待喔
